snippet.title: Initial Wave Trailer
snippet.description:
Initial Wave is a game developed by 3 students from Stadin Ammattiopisto during 2018. 

In Initial Wave you can drive around a fully open world city with destructible objects and 3 different races in different areas that you can complete.

The game also supports local multiplayer with 2 people with either 1 controller and a keyboard or 2 controllers.
